OL,3,CCollecting the dead with nowhere to
OL,4,Cflee: The reality for those left in
OL,5,CRafah
OL,7,FFootage filmed over several days and
OL,8,Fsent to ITV News by one of the last
OL,9,Fjournalists to leave Rafah shows how
OL,10,FIsraeli bombardment has turned the
OL,11,Fcity from a refuge into a terrifying
OL,12,Fdeathtrap for men, women, children and
OL,13,Fwhole families, as ITV News Reporter
OL,14,FChloe Keedy explains
OL,16,FThe streets of Rafah are almost
OL,17,Fcompletely deserted, but Abdullah
OL,18,Fkeeps driving because he has a job to
OL,19,Fdo.
