OL,3,CCollecting the dead with nowhere to
OL,4,Cflee: The reality for those left in
OL,5,CRafah
OL,7,FWhole families lie side by side,
OL,8,Fseparated by sheets of plastic.
OL,10,F"The total number here is 15 from the
OL,11,Fsame family, including many children,"
OL,12,Fa hospital worker explains.
OL,14,F"In just one bag, there is a woman and
OL,15,Fthree kids."
OL,17,FShe says they had come to Rafah to try
OL,18,Fand escape the fighting.
