OL,3,CCollecting the dead with nowhere to
OL,4,Cflee: The reality for those left in
OL,5,CRafah
OL,7,FThe only survivor is a boy called
OL,8,FHazim. He is comforted by his uncle,
OL,9,Fwho is now the closest family he has.
OL,11,F"He lost his mother, three sisters,
OL,12,Fnephews and nieces, who were one, two
OL,13,Fand three years old," his uncle says.
OL,15,F"They are children, unarmed children.
OL,16,FThey say in West Rafah it's safe but
OL,17,Fthere is no safe place here."
