OL,3,CCollecting the dead with nowhere to
OL,4,Cflee: The reality for those left in
OL,5,CRafah
OL,7,FThis city was meant to be Gaza's last
OL,8,Frefuge, but it's now a frontline in
OL,9,FIsrael's war. Rafah's once bustling
OL,10,Fcity centre now stands completely
OL,11,Fabandoned.
OL,13,FStanding alone in the square, Khalid
OL,14,FHamid scarcely recognises the place he
OL,15,Fcalls home.
OL,17,F"I swear to god Rafah is very sad,
OL,18,Fthere is nothing left here," he says.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
