OL,3,CCollecting the dead with nowhere to
OL,4,Cflee: The reality for those left in
OL,5,CRafah
OL,7,FIn Khan Yunis, some families have
OL,8,Fmoved into what's left of a school.
OL,9,FBut all that children are learning
OL,10,Fthere is how to grow up far too fast.
OL,12,FIn Rafah, it's not yet clear what, if
OL,13,Fanything, they will have to come back
OL,14,Fto.
OL,16,FOutside the mortuary, a man sobs in
OL,17,Fsilence as it gets harder and harder
OL,18,Ffor anyone here to find any adequate
OL,19,Fwords.
